      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "The eGFR was calculated using the CKD-EPI equation [CITATION_1] . The unit of SCR in the CKD-EPI formula should be \"mg/dL, \" while the levels of SCR through colorimetric method were in \" mol/L. \" Therefore, we converted SCR according to the formula \"1 mg/dL = 17.1 mol/L\" and put it into the formula to obtain eGFR."
